			<h5>Skinning</h5>
			<p>Your able to skin fur bearing animals you slay.</p>
			<div class="clear"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="professionFrame">
			<div style="float:right; margin-left:20px;" class="qsicons mining"></div>
			<button class="learnProfession" _id="mining">Learn</button>
			<h5>Mining</h5>
			<p>Your keen sense of earth energy allows you to mine ore normally overlooked.</p>
			<div class="clear"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="professionFrame">
